# Terraform AWS Infrastructure with Remote Backend

This project demonstrates Infrastructure as Code (IaC) using Terraform on AWS with remote state management using S3 backend and DynamoDB state locking.

---

## Technologies Used

- Terraform
- AWS EC2
- AWS S3
- AWS DynamoDB
- AWS CLI
- WSL (Ubuntu)

---

## Features

- Provision AWS infrastructure using Terraform
- Remote Terraform state storage using S3
- State locking using DynamoDB
- EC2 instance provisioning
- Terraform outputs and variables
- Infrastructure lifecycle management

