## Terraform Commands

### Initialize Terraform

```bash
terraform init
```

### Validate Configuration

```bash
terraform validate
```

### View Execution Plan

```bash
terraform plan
```

### Apply Infrastructure

```bash
terraform apply
```

### Destroy Infrastructure

```bash
terraform destroy
```

